data.description: PRICE REFRESH - MOTIVATED SELLERS  A cute move-in ready bungalow minutes from downtown OKC and the Plaza District.  Two living spaces, three bedrooms, two baths and a great backyard for entertaining with a pool and a large outdoor storage building. New heating and air in 2014, New roof in 2014, New pool in 2015, New duct work, insulation, floors, fence in 2015, New kitchen and bathroom remodel in 2016.  Garage was converted to make a spacious laundry area and a new master bedroom.   Would make a great starter or perfect for an Airbnb or short-term rental. Home recently appraised for $210k.
